title: Definitions
context: [ยง321-323] Definitions. For the purposes of this part: &ldquo;Preventive health care services&rdquo; means services which promote, enhance, or maintain optimal health and well-being. &ldquo;Target population&rdquo; means women of childbearing age, mothers, families, infants, children, youths, and adolescents.
